9n.text:
This page collects the current Discussion Practices on [3d Arbital], and any debates thereof.

A Discussion Practice is a rule or heuristic of debate and discussion carried out on Arbital.  It includes both generic discussion practices like 'avoid Bulverism', and Arbital-specific practices like 'tag everything that could be related, but if it's only very loosely related, tag it very weakly'.
